\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
\begin_inset Argument 4
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Autarky Equilibrium: PPF
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
For both countries, equilibrium quantities is located where PPF is tangent
 to indifference curve.
 Consumption also equal production in autarky
\end_layout

