\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Under what case will a country experience a drastic change in its relative
 goods price when going from autarky to free trade?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
A country will experience the most drastic change in its relative goods
 price the more 
\emph on
different 
\emph default
it is from the integrated world (post-trade world)
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Different in terms of its stock of factors
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
The country that is most different from the integrated world are the smaller
 countries
\end_layout

\end_deeper
